The paper deals with data management and analytics, which are core topics in the database (cs.DB) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The focus on explaining discrepancies in query results suggests a connection to information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG), where understanding the reasons for differences in results is important. Finally, the use of optimization techniques and algorithms suggests a connection to the data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) sub-category.
